CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 11, 1950, pg. 11, reads: "Recently Married - Mr. and Mrs. Taulton McCullough are among the city's recent newlyweds.  The couple was married on Feb. 25.  The bride is the former Miss Louise Farrish. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Groom Taulton McCullough, and bride Louise Farrish McCullough wearing light colored squiggle patterned suit, posed in front of brick fireplace in living room, with globe on left
